<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Activate Your RubberHeaven Account</title>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

<style type="text/css">
  /* Base */
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    min-width: 100%;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    background-color: #f8fafc;
    color: #334155;
  }

  a {
    color: #3b82f6;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  a:hover {
    color: #1d4ed8;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: #1e293b;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    color: #1e293b;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
  }

  table td {
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  /* Layout */
  .email-wrapper {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .email-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
    padding: 32px 24px;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .email-header::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,0 L100,0 L100,100 Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></svg>');
    background-size: cover;
  }

  .header-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .logo {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .email-body {
    padding: 40px 32px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
  }

  .email-footer {
    background-color: #f1f5f9;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #64748b;
    border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }

  /* Activation Code */
  .activation-code {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
    border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .code {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #0369a1;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
  }

  .code-expiry {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* Button */
  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
    color: #ffffff !important;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }

  .button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 10px -1px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
    .email-body {
      padding: 24px 20px;
    }
    
    .email-header {
      padding: 24px 20px;
    }
    
    .code {
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    
    .button {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    
    <div class="email-header">
      <div class="header-content">
        <div class="logo">RubberHeaven</div>
        <h1>Welcome to RubberHeaven</h1>
        <p style="margin: 0; opacity: 0.9;">Activate your account to get started</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for registering with RubberHeaven. To activate your account and access all our features, please use the following activation code:</p>

      <div class="activation-code">
        <h2 class="code"><%= activationCode %></h2>
        <p class="code-expiry">This code will expire in 5 minutes</p>
      </div>

      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="#" class="button">Activate Account</a>
      </p>

      <p>Enter this code on the activation page to complete your registration. If you did not register for a RubberHeaven account, please disregard this email.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help.</p>
      <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@RubberHeaven.com">support@RubberHeaven.com</a></p>
      <p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> RubberHeaven. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>